             was indicted for <rs id="t18091101-47-off269" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18091101-47-off269" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18091101-47-off269" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18091101-47-cd270" type="crimeDate">26th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091101-47-off269 t18091101-47-cd270"></join>, a watch, value 50 s. and a silver tea spoon, value 2 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18091101-47-victim408" type="victimName">
                        Stephen 
                        Scott
                     <interp inst="t18091101-47-victim408" type="surname" value="Scott"></interp>
